snippet.title: Gravity Crash Ultra -- E3 2014 Trailer (PS Vita)
snippet.description:
The Ultra edition of the PlayStation3 and PlayStation Portable Gravity Crash. This classic retro shooter has been updated to take advantage of the extra GPU power of the PlayStation VITA, there's more particles, more explosions, a remixed soundtrack and all the retro you can handle!

http://www.jawltd.com/gcu/
